# Source DB files stay local — reviewers copy from the challenge package
db/*.db

# Enrichment cache — we commit this one so reviewers don't need Bedrock
# access to see Task 1's output or run the tool tests. It's 16 KB and IS
# the Phase 1 deliverable. Other parquets (if ever added) stay ignored.
data/*.parquet
!data/enriched_movies.parquet

